        <h5>  We are an international group of Fullstack Developers based in Berlin. <strong>Survivors</strong> came to life as a final project for the Web Development Bootcamp @ Le Wagon.</h5>
        <br>
        <h5>  Most apps addressing violence against women primarily use short-term emergency functions - <strong>Survivors</strong> aims to offer a long-term solution to support people that have suffered gender-based violence.</h5>
        <br>
        <h5>  We are a platform that brings together different types of activities and events that help survivors on the journey to recovery and healing after abuse and trauma.</h5>
        <br>
        <h5>  Our vision is to create a community of survivors by providing a place where they can connect and support each other.</h5>
